WEBVTT

01:27.430 --> 01:31.940
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.250 --> 01:34.950
[Episode 7]

02:00.890 --> 02:02.490
-Miss Wang, hurry up.
-Okay.

02:23.120 --> 02:25.320
Which one of you is the killer's parent?

02:25.540 --> 02:27.670
Attorney Zhou and I represent Yuan Ye.

02:27.680 --> 02:28.150
And these two are...

02:28.150 --> 02:30.010
These two are Yuan Ye's teachers.

02:31.030 --> 02:32.240
Sit down. Okay?

02:32.240 --> 02:33.570
Let's sit down and talk.

02:33.800 --> 02:36.120
The killer's parents
don't even dare show up.

02:36.120 --> 02:37.190
What's there to talk about?

02:37.190 --> 02:37.840
Mr. Xu,

02:38.560 --> 02:40.000
it's not that Yuan Ye's parents
didn't want to come,

02:40.000 --> 02:41.400
but they truly couldn't.

02:41.800 --> 02:44.120
Five years ago,
her mother killed her father.

02:44.120 --> 02:45.780
She's currently serving time

02:45.870 --> 02:47.270
for negligent homicide.

02:47.910 --> 02:48.970
I didn't know that.

02:50.630 --> 02:52.829
Look at the kind of people you mess with.

02:53.520 --> 02:54.360
She lied to me.

02:54.800 --> 02:55.400
Stupid.

02:59.190 --> 03:01.520
I am the victim's representative lawyer.

03:01.600 --> 03:04.000
After taking all the actual circumstances
into consideration,

03:04.000 --> 03:06.310
Mr. Xu, in a spirit of generosity,

03:06.840 --> 03:08.590
is willing to propose a settlement
covering medical expenses,

03:08.590 --> 03:10.240
hospitalization meal subsidies,

03:10.240 --> 03:11.590
nursing care, nutrition,

03:11.590 --> 03:13.820
transportation,

03:14.240 --> 03:15.310
and compensation for emotional distress,

03:15.310 --> 03:16.710
totaling 1 million yuan.

03:18.590 --> 03:19.310
Settlement

03:19.470 --> 03:20.800
was proposed by you.

03:20.960 --> 03:22.760
If the conditions cannot be met,

03:23.030 --> 03:24.290
we'll see you in court.

03:24.630 --> 03:25.400
Mr. Xu,

03:26.570 --> 03:28.910
the two of them did have a relationship,

03:29.440 --> 03:30.360
and at the time of the incident

03:30.360 --> 03:31.630
neither side was calm.

03:32.840 --> 03:33.520
Xu Feng,

03:34.310 --> 03:36.520
you wouldn't want your former girlfriend

03:36.520 --> 03:38.720
to spend her youth in prison, would you?

03:40.079 --> 03:42.050
Given my client's special
family circumstances,

03:42.050 --> 03:43.650
1 million is indeed too much.

03:43.750 --> 03:45.550
Then what's there to talk about?

03:48.960 --> 03:49.750
Excuse me.

03:50.630 --> 03:51.760
Can I say a few words?

03:53.470 --> 03:55.380
I didn't introduce myself
properly earlier.

03:55.380 --> 03:57.960
I'm a psychiatrist
at Renxin Municipal Hospital.

03:57.960 --> 03:59.090
My name is Luo Liang.

03:59.690 --> 04:02.190
Attorney Zhou and Xiang invited me
to attend the hearing,

04:02.190 --> 04:04.440
mainly hoping to take this opportunity

04:04.560 --> 04:06.690
for me to explain Yuan Ye's situation.

04:07.400 --> 04:08.600
What Xu Feng just said

04:08.630 --> 04:09.630
was the truth.

04:10.150 --> 04:11.680
When Yuan Ye was dating him,

04:12.000 --> 04:14.260
she did lie about her family background.

04:15.480 --> 04:16.120
Mr. Xu,

04:16.720 --> 04:19.000
young people aren't as
mature and steady as you,

04:19.000 --> 04:20.870
nor have they been through
life's ups and downs.

04:20.870 --> 04:22.630
They're simple and easily trusting—

04:22.630 --> 04:24.030
that's understandable.

04:24.160 --> 04:25.550
It also shows that Xu Feng is,

04:25.550 --> 04:27.310
at heart, kind and sincere,

04:27.740 --> 04:29.270
a testament to your fine upbringing

04:29.270 --> 04:30.470
and his good fortune.

04:31.570 --> 04:32.490
But Yuan Ye

04:34.210 --> 04:36.070
hasn't been nearly as fortunate.

04:36.070 --> 04:37.800
Ever since she was old enough to remember,

04:37.800 --> 04:39.240
she had been dragged around by her mother,

04:39.240 --> 04:40.680
chasing down her father—

04:40.750 --> 04:41.930
trying to catch him cheating,

04:41.930 --> 04:43.330
going after mistresses.

04:48.040 --> 04:49.370
You seduced my husband!

04:53.750 --> 04:56.280
I'll kill you!
How dare you seduce my husband?

04:59.270 --> 05:00.190
You home-wrecker!

05:00.190 --> 05:00.800
Get out!

05:00.950 --> 05:01.620
Get out!

05:02.870 --> 05:03.480
Get out!

05:05.270 --> 05:07.530
You can't keep your own husband in check!

05:09.240 --> 05:10.280
Are you done?

05:10.390 --> 05:12.160
You bring the child every time!

05:15.310 --> 05:17.510
Endless arguments between her parents

05:19.750 --> 05:21.750
and extremely irrational violence

05:21.830 --> 05:22.560
and beatings

05:24.720 --> 05:26.650
were her main childhood memories.

05:30.430 --> 05:31.380
Excuse me,

05:32.620 --> 05:33.430
is there

05:33.430 --> 05:35.040
a girl named Yuan Ye living around here?

05:35.040 --> 05:36.470
Yes, on the third floor.

05:36.870 --> 05:37.870
Until 5 years ago,

05:38.270 --> 05:39.800
Yuan Ye, having just graduated from
a vocational high school,

05:39.800 --> 05:41.540
witnessed her mother,

05:41.670 --> 05:44.750
unable to tolerate her
repeatedly cheating father anymore,

05:44.750 --> 05:45.830
grab an axe

05:46.340 --> 05:47.220
in a fit of rage

05:48.090 --> 05:49.420
and hack at her husband,

05:50.000 --> 05:50.909
thus

05:51.400 --> 05:53.330
causing an irreversible tragedy.

06:01.190 --> 06:02.450
This unfortunate girl

06:03.040 --> 06:04.160
has never experienced

06:04.160 --> 06:06.240
a healthy relationship.

06:07.360 --> 06:08.560
She yearned for love,

06:09.190 --> 06:10.790
but doesn't know how to love.

06:11.480 --> 06:12.280
What she needs

06:12.750 --> 06:14.080
is not just punishment,

06:14.610 --> 06:16.990
but perhaps more guidance and help.

06:17.750 --> 06:20.150
Just as Mr. Xu questioned
at the beginning,

06:20.390 --> 06:22.120
none of us are Yuan Ye's family.

06:22.220 --> 06:23.670
But we came here today,

06:23.920 --> 06:25.920
primarily hoping to act on her behalf

06:25.920 --> 06:27.480
to seek your forgiveness.

06:28.080 --> 06:28.680
After all,

06:28.870 --> 06:31.330
her childhood and birth
were not her choice.

06:31.630 --> 06:32.560
But you

06:33.270 --> 06:35.770
can give a child
who has temporarily gone astray

06:35.770 --> 06:37.680
a chance to start over.

06:40.120 --> 06:40.830
Please.

06:42.750 --> 06:43.159
Mr. Xu.

06:45.560 --> 06:46.600
You mean

06:47.120 --> 06:49.180
she is justified because she is weak,

06:49.270 --> 06:49.950
so our

06:49.950 --> 06:50.750
carefully raised,

06:50.750 --> 06:51.870
healthy kids

06:52.390 --> 06:53.870
deserve to be hurt by her?

06:54.510 --> 06:56.970
If being excusable means being forgivable,

06:57.300 --> 06:58.630
then what is the law for?

07:01.120 --> 07:01.630
Xu Feng,

07:02.680 --> 07:03.540
what do you say?

07:14.610 --> 07:15.980
Teaching her a lesson

07:17.410 --> 07:18.870
is the best choice for her.

07:21.870 --> 07:22.510
Xu Feng,

07:23.030 --> 07:24.390
you repeatedly

07:24.680 --> 07:26.610
dated several girls at the same time.

07:26.610 --> 07:29.040
You deliberately
provoked Yuan Ye's emotions.

07:29.040 --> 07:31.170
But she was completely sincere to you.

07:31.810 --> 07:33.560
Even now, she is still

07:33.750 --> 07:35.310
suffering and blaming herself
for hurting you,

07:35.310 --> 07:36.770
and wishing she were dead.

07:37.720 --> 07:39.780
Don't you have any compassion at all?

07:42.310 --> 07:44.000
Is it illegal to date

07:44.070 --> 07:45.800
multiple girlfriends at once?

07:46.040 --> 07:47.600
They were only with him

07:48.040 --> 07:50.190
because he had my money in his pocket.

07:50.720 --> 07:51.950
Now that they've broken up,

07:51.950 --> 07:53.810
she goes crazy and stabs someone;

07:53.950 --> 07:55.070
does a person like her

07:55.070 --> 07:56.330
deserve any sympathy?

08:03.190 --> 08:03.720
Xu Feng,

08:04.720 --> 08:06.450
can I have a word with you alone?

08:33.159 --> 08:33.809
Sorry.

08:34.630 --> 08:36.030
I couldn't be of any help.

08:36.470 --> 08:37.470
You did your best.

08:38.360 --> 08:39.950
It was actually expected.

08:40.950 --> 08:43.280
The victim's family isn't short on money,

08:44.030 --> 08:45.510
and judging from their attitude,

08:45.510 --> 08:47.840
there's hardly any room for negotiation.

08:56.550 --> 08:57.550
Here's the thing.

08:58.230 --> 08:59.200
Mr. Xu and his son

08:59.550 --> 09:01.680
have taken the other family's
circumstances into consideration.

09:01.680 --> 09:03.680
They've agreed to reduce the compensation

09:03.680 --> 09:06.000
and have signed a letter of understanding.

09:06.000 --> 09:07.560
As for the specific settlement terms,

09:07.560 --> 09:09.960
I'll be handling the negotiations in full.

09:11.800 --> 09:13.830
What exactly did you say to Xu Feng?

09:14.200 --> 09:16.200
A few words made him change his mind.

09:17.590 --> 09:19.450
I didn't actually say much to him.

09:20.790 --> 09:21.850
Have you ever heard

09:22.360 --> 09:24.490
of intergenerational transmission?

09:24.600 --> 09:25.530
What do you mean?

09:25.600 --> 09:27.510
It means the parents' behaviors and ideas

09:27.510 --> 09:29.840
are subtly passed down to their children.

09:30.200 --> 09:32.200
Yuan Ye's mother killed her father.

09:32.250 --> 09:33.500
If Yuan Ye finds out

09:33.630 --> 09:35.270
that Xu Feng doesn't forgive her

09:35.270 --> 09:37.270
and even agrees to let her go to jail,

09:37.370 --> 09:38.770
it could cause a huge blow

09:38.870 --> 09:40.360
to Yuan Ye's mind.

09:41.010 --> 09:42.360
Maybe after she gets out of prison,

09:42.360 --> 09:44.220
she won't let Xu Feng off the hook.

09:44.770 --> 09:45.630
I just explained

09:45.630 --> 09:47.040
this concept to Xu Feng.

09:50.840 --> 09:51.910
I knew it.

09:52.630 --> 09:54.810
People like you who have moral obsessions

09:54.810 --> 09:56.720
would never accept me saying that.

09:56.720 --> 09:57.440
No, no.

09:58.390 --> 10:00.250
Actually, I could guess a little.

10:00.270 --> 10:02.070
Because after you talked to him,

10:02.410 --> 10:04.740
I saw fear in his eyes.

10:05.120 --> 10:06.250
He should be afraid.

10:07.790 --> 10:08.790
Making him afraid

10:09.840 --> 10:12.000
finally got us a decent result.

10:12.660 --> 10:14.120
Shouldn't we celebrate

10:14.120 --> 10:15.250
and have a nice meal?

10:15.920 --> 10:17.950
I really should treat you to a nice meal

10:17.950 --> 10:19.010
to appreciate you.

10:19.510 --> 10:20.510
I didn't even know

10:20.870 --> 10:23.800
you went to investigate
Yuan Ye's family situation.

10:24.140 --> 10:25.340
Do you remember this?

10:26.680 --> 10:27.760
What is it?

10:29.550 --> 10:31.670
The first time we went to Xu Feng's school

10:31.670 --> 10:32.630
and met Yuan Ye,

10:32.870 --> 10:33.550
didn't you get really angry

10:33.550 --> 10:35.410
and slam a lighter onto the table?

10:37.840 --> 10:39.440
I've been to this nightclub.

10:39.750 --> 10:41.610
It turns out Yuan Ye worked there.

10:42.010 --> 10:43.870
Then I found out about her family,

10:44.150 --> 10:47.010
and learned they had
this kind of story behind them.

10:47.520 --> 10:48.760
Really, thank you

10:49.840 --> 10:51.240
for doing so much for her.

10:51.710 --> 10:52.460
But...

10:55.480 --> 10:57.540
After all that buildup of gratitude,

10:57.720 --> 10:59.510
aren't you just leading up to saying

10:59.510 --> 11:02.190
you don't have time
to have dinner with me?

11:03.390 --> 11:03.960
No, no.

11:04.070 --> 11:05.050
Actually, it's okay.

11:05.050 --> 11:07.740
Every time I ask you out for a meal,
I'm just pushing my luck.

11:07.740 --> 11:09.790
I'm already very used to
being rejected by you.

11:09.790 --> 11:11.120
That's not what I meant.

11:11.440 --> 11:12.150
By the way,

11:18.550 --> 11:20.360
I washed your clothes.

11:20.480 --> 11:21.190
Thank you.

11:21.240 --> 11:21.970
That's good.

11:22.120 --> 11:23.250
I'll pick the place.

11:23.370 --> 11:25.400
I'll take this time to go home,

11:25.420 --> 11:27.350
take a shower, and change clothes.

11:28.230 --> 11:29.760
Does it have to be so formal?

11:30.030 --> 11:32.410
Of course. The sense of ceremony
is important.

11:32.410 --> 11:34.240
We can't just meet every time

11:34.240 --> 11:36.030
dressed like we're going to work.

11:36.030 --> 11:38.440
You can always put on a nice outfit

11:38.440 --> 11:40.000
and have a relaxing meal.

11:41.670 --> 11:44.470
Then I have to go home and change.

11:44.660 --> 11:46.120
Dinner will be even later.

11:46.440 --> 11:47.040
It's okay.

11:48.160 --> 11:49.820
To see a different side of you,

11:50.440 --> 11:51.610
it's worth the wait.

11:55.360 --> 11:57.270
[Police]

12:00.030 --> 12:05.750
[The chips are delicious.
The chips are delicious.]

12:11.470 --> 12:13.500
[China Police]

12:13.570 --> 12:17.220
[The chips are delicious.
The chips are delicious.]

12:20.630 --> 12:22.130
No wonder.

12:23.390 --> 12:24.120
Wait, you...

12:26.610 --> 12:27.650
Aren't you the...

12:28.630 --> 12:29.760
You're our comrade.

12:30.270 --> 12:30.960
What's up?

12:31.780 --> 12:32.700
[China Police]

12:33.240 --> 12:33.590
[Name: Pongsri Leekpa]

12:35.840 --> 12:36.970
How do you have this?

12:43.150 --> 12:44.750
It's exactly the same. Look.

12:46.150 --> 12:46.880
Come with me.

12:48.360 --> 12:49.420
Where are we going?

12:57.210 --> 13:02.560
[China Police]

13:17.010 --> 13:18.870
Does the task force provide food?

13:19.390 --> 13:19.790
Yes.

13:22.260 --> 13:23.840
Can I use my institute meal card

13:23.840 --> 13:25.200
in the task force?

13:25.200 --> 13:25.840
No.

13:30.120 --> 13:30.720
It's fine.

13:35.980 --> 13:36.910
Clear this area.

13:39.360 --> 13:40.290
Clear this area.

13:44.080 --> 13:44.720
Who is it?

13:47.360 --> 13:48.420
What are you doing?

13:49.700 --> 13:51.570
We just finished eating.

13:51.710 --> 13:52.720
Hold it up!

13:52.720 --> 13:53.440
This...

13:54.910 --> 13:56.570
You're playing a game, right?

13:57.550 --> 13:59.050
I'm not going to scold you.

13:59.070 --> 14:00.330
Why are you so nervous?

14:00.390 --> 14:01.510
It's a new game.

14:01.900 --> 14:03.750
Dad and I have been waiting for days.

14:03.750 --> 14:05.070
We make a great team.

14:05.270 --> 14:06.450
Listen to Dad.

14:06.750 --> 14:08.210
I'm home. I'll hang up now.

14:25.240 --> 14:25.840
Dr. Luo,

14:25.840 --> 14:26.600
I'm home.

14:29.320 --> 14:29.910
Don't move.

14:29.910 --> 14:31.360
Who are you? What are you doing?

14:31.360 --> 14:32.960
Is there anyone else in the house?

14:32.960 --> 14:33.440
Yes!

14:34.960 --> 14:35.820
Where are they?

14:36.480 --> 14:37.080
Come out!

14:37.670 --> 14:39.030
People in the room, come out!

14:39.030 --> 14:39.790
Liu Ping?

14:42.840 --> 14:43.770
What do you want?

14:43.870 --> 14:45.200
I'm calling the police!

14:45.510 --> 14:46.480
You dare call the police?

14:46.480 --> 14:47.880
You dare call the police?

14:48.030 --> 14:49.430
You dare call the police?

14:49.480 --> 14:50.910
Tell me, where is she?

14:51.510 --> 14:53.040
Where did you hide Yu Kexin?

14:53.550 --> 14:53.950
She...

14:54.120 --> 14:56.200
She went back to Australia
to find her mom.

14:56.200 --> 14:58.080
Bullshit! What Australia?

14:58.080 --> 14:59.080
What Mom?

14:59.100 --> 15:00.950
You are all lying to me!

15:01.270 --> 15:02.470
Why would I lie to you?

15:02.670 --> 15:03.800
What did I lie about?

15:04.150 --> 15:06.210
I personally took her to the airport.

15:06.550 --> 15:08.810
I saw her walk in with my own eyes.

15:09.840 --> 15:10.960
Please calm down.

15:11.180 --> 15:12.310
Don't be impulsive.

15:12.960 --> 15:14.580
Put the knife down, okay?

15:15.960 --> 15:17.960
She's still pregnant with your child.

15:17.960 --> 15:19.840
She wouldn't lie to you.

15:19.960 --> 15:22.840
Bullshit! What child?

15:22.960 --> 15:24.240
It's all fake!

15:25.390 --> 15:27.120
I don't even know

15:27.120 --> 15:28.450
if I've ever had a child.

15:33.440 --> 15:34.680
What do you mean?

15:37.120 --> 15:38.320
I don't understand.

15:42.910 --> 15:45.320
After we finalized the divorce,
I moved out.

15:45.320 --> 15:46.000
A few days ago,

15:46.000 --> 15:48.060
property management called and said

15:48.200 --> 15:49.720
the bathroom was leaking

15:50.120 --> 15:52.320
and flooded the apartment downstairs.

15:52.550 --> 15:54.510
So I tried to get it fixed.

15:55.360 --> 15:56.590
But when I called her,

15:56.840 --> 15:59.080
the number was out of service.

15:59.670 --> 16:02.390
I checked and she canceled the number.

16:02.720 --> 16:04.390
So I had to rush home.

16:04.720 --> 16:07.120
I found out she had moved out
a long time ago.

16:08.320 --> 16:09.440
She just left a key

16:09.440 --> 16:12.100
with the property management
to sell the house.

16:12.390 --> 16:13.360
That's normal.

16:14.270 --> 16:17.330
She probably wanted to
make a clean break with the past.

16:17.510 --> 16:19.150
I thought so too at first,

16:19.550 --> 16:21.120
but then I found this.

16:24.660 --> 16:25.430
What is this?

16:26.120 --> 16:28.080
It's a benzodiazepine-based,

16:28.080 --> 16:30.080
highly potent sedative-hypnotic.

16:30.270 --> 16:32.960
It's a strictly controlled
psychotropic drug.

16:33.150 --> 16:35.630
It is commonly known as
obedience powder or date rape pills.

16:35.630 --> 16:37.670
It's even more potent
when mixed with alcohol.

16:37.670 --> 16:38.550
Looking at this packaging,

16:38.550 --> 16:40.670
it might have been illegally imported
from abroad.

16:40.670 --> 16:41.480
Xinxin,

16:42.870 --> 16:44.480
get me a glass of water.

16:49.390 --> 16:50.320
Xinxin!

17:03.480 --> 17:04.160
Xinxin!

17:05.589 --> 17:06.310
Xinxin!

17:07.440 --> 17:08.109
Xinxin!

17:12.400 --> 17:13.000
Xinxin!

17:17.920 --> 17:19.349
You mean

17:20.349 --> 17:22.200
Yu Kexin gave you this drug

17:23.000 --> 17:25.329
and then faked a domestic violence scene?

17:25.750 --> 17:26.109
Then,

17:26.750 --> 17:28.750
what about the injuries on her body?

17:29.920 --> 17:31.980
She couldn't have beaten herself up?

17:32.070 --> 17:34.620
Anyway, it definitely wasn't me.

17:35.160 --> 17:36.290
The doctor also said

17:36.640 --> 17:38.660
that this medicine
knocks you out completely.

17:38.660 --> 17:40.310
I had no ability to move at all.

17:40.310 --> 17:42.710
How could I have the strength
to hit anyone?

17:43.160 --> 17:44.160
How could someone

17:45.110 --> 17:46.880
be so cruel to themselves?

17:48.400 --> 17:49.880
She's also pregnant.

17:53.110 --> 17:55.070
The domestic abuse was fake—

17:56.030 --> 17:57.830
how could the pregnancy be real?

17:58.680 --> 18:00.270
Later, I checked

18:01.000 --> 18:02.260
every OB-GYN hospital

18:02.400 --> 18:04.510
in Lihai City.

18:04.510 --> 18:05.640
There's no record of

18:05.640 --> 18:08.310
her ever visiting

18:08.720 --> 18:10.380
or registering at any of them.

18:13.200 --> 18:15.200
The most important thing for you now

18:15.270 --> 18:16.870
is to take care of your health

18:16.880 --> 18:18.310
and stay emotionally stable.

18:18.310 --> 18:21.110
After all, you're responsible for
two people now.

18:24.750 --> 18:26.400
I can raise you on my own,

18:27.160 --> 18:27.990
can't I?

18:29.070 --> 18:30.350
This is too absurd.

18:30.960 --> 18:32.100
She came to me

18:32.550 --> 18:33.790
to borrow money

18:33.790 --> 18:35.110
so she could hide out for a few days.

18:35.110 --> 18:35.820
She said

18:36.240 --> 18:37.720
all her money was with you.

18:38.590 --> 18:39.920
I've seen her Weibo.

18:40.440 --> 18:41.570
She's quite wealthy

18:42.200 --> 18:43.330
and even has a house.

18:44.850 --> 18:48.070
[Clairet Xin, Stay Happy]

18:48.730 --> 18:50.530
She deleted all her Weibo posts.

18:54.960 --> 18:57.550
Later, I went to that so-called home

18:57.550 --> 18:58.410
to look for her.

18:59.000 --> 19:00.860
She said her mom bought it for her,

19:02.110 --> 19:03.030
but actually,

19:03.680 --> 19:05.200
that house was rented

19:05.720 --> 19:07.780
and only for a little over two months.

19:08.790 --> 19:09.990
After we got married,

19:10.960 --> 19:12.820
it was always me giving her money.

19:13.510 --> 19:15.710
She didn't leave a single penny with me.

19:17.310 --> 19:18.000
The tattoo.

19:19.070 --> 19:20.930
I found you because of the tattoo.

19:22.440 --> 19:24.110
She said you got that tattoo

19:24.750 --> 19:26.270
for her.

19:27.590 --> 19:29.640
Did you know she took out a nude loan?

19:31.400 --> 19:32.480
What nude loan?

19:34.200 --> 19:35.070
She made me

19:35.440 --> 19:37.000
get this tattoo when we got married—

19:37.000 --> 19:39.390
kept pushing me until I gave in,

19:39.720 --> 19:41.440
said it was to commemorate our love.

19:41.440 --> 19:42.160
This...

19:43.590 --> 19:45.130
Liu Ping, aren't you disgusted?

19:45.130 --> 19:46.900
I never thought you were
this kind of person.

19:46.900 --> 19:47.830
No, no.

19:48.400 --> 19:49.070
Xinxin.

19:49.070 --> 19:49.800
Listen to me.

19:49.960 --> 19:50.350
Xinxin.

19:50.350 --> 19:51.030
Don't touch me!

19:51.030 --> 19:52.090
Xinxin, I'm not...

19:52.550 --> 19:54.590
It's really not what you think.

19:54.720 --> 19:55.750
I called a few

19:55.750 --> 19:57.160
colleagues

19:57.160 --> 19:59.460
who were working overtime,
both men and women.

19:59.460 --> 20:02.190
Are female colleagues
necessarily good people?

20:02.510 --> 20:04.550
If there's really nothing between you two,

20:04.550 --> 20:06.440
why is her hair on you?

20:06.440 --> 20:08.480
I... I don't know either.

20:08.480 --> 20:09.340
You don't know?

20:10.070 --> 20:10.960
Xinxin.

20:11.030 --> 20:13.400
Calm down.

20:13.510 --> 20:13.880
I...

20:14.480 --> 20:15.120
Phone.

20:15.720 --> 20:16.230
Phone.

20:16.720 --> 20:17.240
Phone.

20:17.310 --> 20:18.000
Here.

20:19.880 --> 20:21.440
I'll call your colleagues right now.

20:21.440 --> 20:22.510
I'll call them one by one

20:22.510 --> 20:23.590
and ask them clearly

20:23.590 --> 20:24.680
what exactly is going on!

20:24.680 --> 20:25.480
Xinxin, I beg you.

20:25.480 --> 20:26.070
Calm down.

20:26.070 --> 20:27.720
Really. We're married.

20:27.720 --> 20:29.440
I couldn't possibly be involved with
another woman.

20:29.440 --> 20:29.880
Is that so?

20:29.880 --> 20:30.550
Then swear it.

20:30.550 --> 20:31.640
I swear.

20:31.830 --> 20:34.110
I, Liu Ping,

20:34.110 --> 20:35.750
I swear, well...

20:35.750 --> 20:37.210
You can't even swear properly!

20:37.210 --> 20:39.200
Do you think just talking is enough?

20:39.200 --> 20:40.480
Why should I believe you?

20:40.480 --> 20:41.240
I...

20:41.920 --> 20:44.580
I'm asking you
how you're going to prove it to me.

20:45.200 --> 20:46.070
Xinxin.

20:46.070 --> 20:47.400
Xinxin, calm down.

20:47.480 --> 20:49.790
Xinxin, don't be angry anymore.

20:52.070 --> 20:53.110
I'll prove it

20:53.110 --> 20:54.370
however you want me to.

20:55.240 --> 20:56.400
Don't be angry anymore.

20:56.400 --> 20:57.330
I'm begging you.

20:58.640 --> 20:59.770
Then go get a tattoo.

21:00.750 --> 21:01.280
A tattoo?

21:04.820 --> 21:07.080
Get the exact same design tattooed on you

21:07.240 --> 21:08.300
to prove you love me

21:08.460 --> 21:10.430
and that you belong only to me.

21:10.590 --> 21:11.480
If any woman

21:11.480 --> 21:12.830
sees this design on you,

21:12.830 --> 21:14.440
I curse the two of you adulterers

21:14.440 --> 21:15.770
to die a horrible death.

21:19.270 --> 21:19.940
Xinxin.

21:22.030 --> 21:23.020
You don't agree?

21:25.160 --> 21:25.590
No.

21:28.110 --> 21:29.440
I want you to get a tattoo

21:30.200 --> 21:32.200
just to prove you love me

21:33.200 --> 21:34.860
and that you belong only to me.

21:37.200 --> 21:38.510
Because I love Leilei.

21:39.480 --> 21:40.240
Since I love her,

21:40.240 --> 21:41.310
I must love all of her,

21:41.310 --> 21:43.270
including her flaws.

21:43.590 --> 21:44.720
I was forced by the creditors

21:44.720 --> 21:47.470
to get a tattoo as they demanded.

21:47.510 --> 21:48.930
The tattoo on Leilei

21:49.830 --> 21:51.350
was probably also done

21:51.350 --> 21:52.810
as these people demanded.

21:57.110 --> 21:58.710
Hello. Is Officer Li there?

21:58.920 --> 21:59.810
Who is this?

21:59.960 --> 22:01.000
My name is Yan Ling.

22:01.000 --> 22:02.350
I'm a friend of a client

22:02.350 --> 22:03.400
from one of his previous cases.

22:03.400 --> 22:05.400
I have some information to tell him.

22:05.920 --> 22:07.680
He's left for the provincial department.

22:07.680 --> 22:08.610
He left?

22:08.790 --> 22:09.960
The task force is confidential.

22:09.960 --> 22:11.090
He can't be reached.

22:11.160 --> 22:11.960
You can't get away.

22:11.960 --> 22:12.790
Let me tell you,

22:12.790 --> 22:14.350
I'm not done with you today.

22:14.440 --> 22:15.510
-You can't get away.
-What are you doing?

22:15.510 --> 22:16.270
Someone!

22:16.290 --> 22:20.650
[Police]

22:20.970 --> 22:23.820
[110 Emergency Call Center – Service Hall]

22:31.110 --> 22:33.740
Hello. The number you dialed
is out of service.

22:33.820 --> 22:35.420
Please check and dial again.

22:42.510 --> 22:45.210
Hello. The number you dialed
is out of service.

22:45.240 --> 22:46.840
Please check and dial again.

22:54.400 --> 22:55.510
I was forced by the creditors

22:55.510 --> 22:56.370
to follow their

22:56.880 --> 22:58.280
demands and get a tattoo.

22:58.380 --> 22:59.850
I even held my ID card

23:00.240 --> 23:01.880
and took those kinds of photos.

23:01.880 --> 23:02.920
What nude loan?

23:03.030 --> 23:04.160
He said he felt sorry for me.

23:04.160 --> 23:05.190
So I figured

23:08.310 --> 23:09.510
she was probably just
following their instructions...

23:09.510 --> 23:10.480
To witness our love...

23:10.480 --> 23:11.480
Then he went and got the same tattoo

23:11.480 --> 23:12.520
as me.

23:18.240 --> 23:21.920
[Police]

23:41.510 --> 23:42.550
I'm sorry.

23:43.240 --> 23:45.420
I had so many things to do today.

23:45.750 --> 23:46.440
I'm late.

23:46.440 --> 23:47.900
Sorry to keep you waiting.

23:48.750 --> 23:49.960
You are really busy.

23:50.400 --> 23:51.070
I

23:52.270 --> 23:53.270
can tell.

23:58.640 --> 23:59.510
Are you okay?

24:04.980 --> 24:06.080
It's all my fault.

24:07.200 --> 24:09.250
I felt like I was drugged.

24:10.120 --> 24:12.150
I believed whatever Yu Kexin said.

24:12.680 --> 24:13.680
This Yu Kexin

24:13.970 --> 24:15.500
seems to know you very well.

24:16.000 --> 24:18.160
She hits all your weak spots.

24:19.070 --> 24:20.920
She lost her father in childhood,

24:20.920 --> 24:22.920
met the wrong guy like Li Changning,

24:23.200 --> 24:24.920
and both were pitifully hurt.

24:26.740 --> 24:29.270
She said the tattoo
was because of a nude loan,

24:29.680 --> 24:32.080
and Xia Yi said the same thing
about Leilei.

24:32.700 --> 24:33.960
And I just believed it.

24:35.150 --> 24:36.700
I didn't even question it.

24:37.350 --> 24:38.750
Maybe they are all liars.

24:39.490 --> 24:41.020
Could they know each other?

24:42.550 --> 24:44.580
Xia Yi is Leilei's ex-boyfriend.

24:44.920 --> 24:47.050
Leilei must have mentioned you to him.

24:47.480 --> 24:49.080
They exchanged information

24:49.310 --> 24:50.830
and plugged all the holes

24:50.830 --> 24:52.370
that would make you suspicious.

24:52.370 --> 24:54.500
At the same time, they used your guilt,

24:54.840 --> 24:56.270
because you are still
in grief and self-blame

24:56.270 --> 24:58.420
over losing Leilei.

24:58.440 --> 25:00.020
So it's easier to believe

25:00.510 --> 25:02.840
Yu Kexin, who faked a similar experience.

25:08.870 --> 25:11.070
What I can't forgive myself for the most

25:11.790 --> 25:13.270
is how I could believe

25:14.110 --> 25:15.000
that Leilei

25:15.550 --> 25:17.950
would get a tattoo,
and take out a nude loan.

25:22.680 --> 25:23.680
Do you feel

25:25.590 --> 25:27.050
that you betrayed Leilei?

25:34.030 --> 25:36.110
How could I doubt Leilei like this?

25:37.070 --> 25:39.000
I'm her best friend.

26:00.550 --> 26:01.590
Drink less.

26:02.150 --> 26:04.350
Getting drunk won't solve the problem.

26:07.400 --> 26:07.860
Listen,

26:10.000 --> 26:10.880
we are human.

26:11.440 --> 26:13.960
Making mistakes is our factory setting.

26:14.660 --> 26:15.450
What's more,

26:16.060 --> 26:18.670
this scam was tailor-made for you.

26:19.060 --> 26:20.450
If it were any of us,

26:20.480 --> 26:22.940
it'd be hard to guarantee
not being scammed.

26:23.440 --> 26:25.240
Don't blame yourself like this.

26:29.470 --> 26:30.930
You act like a superwoman,

26:31.370 --> 26:33.940
trying your best to protect Li Changning,

26:34.160 --> 26:34.720
Yuan Ye,

26:34.990 --> 26:36.700
and even Yu Kexin.

26:37.270 --> 26:38.160
Do you know why?

26:44.860 --> 26:47.720
You blame yourself
for your best friend's suicide,

26:47.990 --> 26:49.720
and that's why.

26:53.440 --> 26:55.240
You are trying hard to make up for

26:55.830 --> 26:57.880
the regret of not helping Leilei.

27:03.960 --> 27:05.680
Those who always save others

27:07.850 --> 27:08.650
are actually

27:09.680 --> 27:10.960
saving themselves.

27:15.890 --> 27:18.020
I don't know what you've been through.

27:21.030 --> 27:22.290
But I always feel that,

27:23.680 --> 27:25.640
subconsciously,

27:27.440 --> 27:28.990
when you hit rock bottom

27:29.350 --> 27:30.590
and are in deep pain,

27:32.310 --> 27:34.260
you yearn for someone like you

27:36.240 --> 27:37.640
to reach out and help you.

27:44.480 --> 27:45.740
I want to tell you that,

27:47.550 --> 27:48.610
if you are willing,

27:50.960 --> 27:51.820
I will be there.

28:29.510 --> 28:30.400
Ling!

28:32.350 --> 28:32.750
Ling.

28:34.590 --> 28:35.480
Ling!

28:36.030 --> 28:36.920
Ling!

28:42.160 --> 28:42.750
No!

28:43.030 --> 28:44.270
Let me go!

28:45.440 --> 28:46.920
Let me go!

28:48.040 --> 28:50.000
I don't need you! Go away!

28:59.920 --> 29:01.880
I know you are suffering.

29:02.270 --> 29:04.120
I know you miss him.

29:05.270 --> 29:06.200
But he wouldn't want to

29:06.200 --> 29:08.540
see you like this from heaven.

29:10.790 --> 29:12.920
If your father saw you like this now,

29:13.000 --> 29:14.650
he would be very sad.

29:14.790 --> 29:16.750
He would be even sadder than you.

29:17.440 --> 29:18.820
You still have me.

29:20.000 --> 29:21.530
Yan Ling, you still have me.

29:23.000 --> 29:24.870
You still have me, Yan Ling.

29:26.590 --> 29:27.590
Leilei.

29:28.310 --> 29:29.310
Leilei.

29:30.310 --> 29:31.510
Don't worry, Leilei.

29:32.270 --> 29:33.880
This is not over yet.

29:34.710 --> 29:36.640
I will definitely clear your name.

29:40.500 --> 29:42.350
[Dream Traveler, Traveler Quadrant]
[Liu Ping, Kexin]

29:47.780 --> 29:49.990
[Pongsri Leekpa, Pazion, Xia Yi]

29:59.740 --> 30:04.950
[Lihai Tattoo Forum]

30:07.530 --> 30:11.600
[Lihai Tattoo Forum]

30:09.160 --> 30:11.790
This tattoo of an eye and an octopus

30:11.960 --> 30:12.890
is so beautiful.

30:12.920 --> 30:14.450
He knows about this tattoo.

30:21.640 --> 30:23.570
You know it's an octopus and an eye.

30:24.790 --> 30:26.990
Where did you learn about this pattern?

30:28.560 --> 30:30.180
[Who knows this tattoo?]

30:30.180 --> 30:31.840
[Eric]

30:33.440 --> 30:34.640
If you see my message,

30:35.310 --> 30:36.770
please make sure to reply.

30:44.580 --> 30:47.920
[Xinsheng International Law Firm]

30:52.820 --> 30:53.680
I'm sorry.

30:54.640 --> 30:55.750
I'm sorry, Senior.

30:56.510 --> 30:57.990
I was too gullible.

30:58.750 --> 31:00.720
I introduced a scammer to you all.

31:00.960 --> 31:02.690
Right now, I just want to be able

31:02.720 --> 31:04.240
to find this Yu Kexin.

31:04.440 --> 31:06.880
This way, not only can I
give Liu Ping an explanation,

31:06.880 --> 31:07.920
but I can also help my friend

31:07.920 --> 31:09.550
find the person who scammed her.

31:09.550 --> 31:11.000
I once told you that

31:11.750 --> 31:14.350
Yu Kexin seems capable of
protecting herself.

31:14.440 --> 31:16.590
She's not as innocent as you thought.

31:17.160 --> 31:18.470
But she is my client.

31:18.880 --> 31:20.560
Everything she provided

31:20.590 --> 31:22.120
must be kept confidential.

31:22.160 --> 31:24.000
Even after our client relationship ends,

31:24.000 --> 31:25.240
I still must keep it confidential.

31:25.240 --> 31:26.350
That's the law.

31:27.200 --> 31:28.000
I know.

31:28.350 --> 31:28.720
Well,

31:29.720 --> 31:31.240
so there's really nothing

31:31.240 --> 31:32.270
we can do to her?

31:32.960 --> 31:33.880
From marriage,

31:34.200 --> 31:34.800
to divorce

31:35.000 --> 31:35.750
to the division of assets,

31:35.750 --> 31:37.440
everything she did was legal.

31:38.400 --> 31:39.960
Unless Liu Ping can prove

31:39.960 --> 31:41.480
the domestic abuse never happened,

31:41.480 --> 31:42.880
or that Yu Kexin's motive

31:43.110 --> 31:44.270
for marrying was solely to divorce

31:44.270 --> 31:45.680
and take the property,

31:46.070 --> 31:47.640
we have no legal leverage

31:47.640 --> 31:49.240
against her.

31:49.240 --> 31:50.440
But she obviously...

31:54.790 --> 31:55.650
Attorney Zhou,

31:55.750 --> 31:58.110
Yu Kexin executed everything
so flawlessly.

31:58.110 --> 31:59.910
You can tell she's experienced.

31:59.950 --> 32:02.600
She's definitely going to
find her next target,

32:02.600 --> 32:04.730
and more people will end up being hurt.

32:12.750 --> 32:14.880
Let me give you a little legal insight.

32:15.160 --> 32:17.110
Do you know how insurance is divided

32:17.110 --> 32:18.830
after a divorce?

32:23.270 --> 32:25.090
According to our country's Insurance Law,

32:25.090 --> 32:27.070
there must be an insurable interest

32:27.070 --> 32:28.680
between the policyholder and the insured.

32:28.680 --> 32:29.790
After a divorce,

32:30.240 --> 32:31.680
that relationship disappears,

32:31.680 --> 32:33.830
so the insurable interest
no longer exists.

32:33.830 --> 32:34.710
At this point,

32:34.920 --> 32:37.480
if the policyholder and the insured

32:37.480 --> 32:38.960
are not the same person,

32:39.070 --> 32:41.440
the policy needs to be updated.

32:51.200 --> 32:52.590
You mean

32:53.640 --> 32:55.160
they purchased insurance

32:55.830 --> 32:56.400
and then changed

32:56.400 --> 32:57.510
the beneficiary

32:57.510 --> 32:58.010
during

32:58.310 --> 32:59.680
the property division?

33:00.440 --> 33:02.310
Regarding customer privacy,

33:02.560 --> 33:03.560
I have no comment.

33:06.360 --> 33:07.420
This is it.

33:07.920 --> 33:09.900
This is the insurance company.

33:10.270 --> 33:12.600
She brought the brochure back then.

33:13.070 --> 33:13.720
She said

33:14.200 --> 33:15.880
she was both the policyholder

33:15.880 --> 33:16.960
and the insured,

33:16.960 --> 33:18.420
and I was the beneficiary.

33:18.790 --> 33:20.350
She told me that if she ever got sick
or there was some disaster,

33:20.350 --> 33:21.830
I'd still get a sum of money.

33:21.830 --> 33:23.680
Even though I paid for the insurance,

33:23.680 --> 33:25.310
I was really touched at the time.

33:25.310 --> 33:27.240
Do you remember how this insurance

33:27.270 --> 33:29.640
was divided when you divorced?

33:29.790 --> 33:31.000
It wasn't divided.

33:31.000 --> 33:32.460
I gave all the money to her.

33:32.470 --> 33:33.680
Even though her lawyer said

33:33.680 --> 33:35.910
I had the right to take back

33:36.010 --> 33:37.510
50% of the benefits,

33:37.510 --> 33:38.000
I didn't

33:38.160 --> 33:38.620
want it.

33:40.830 --> 33:42.440
But changing the beneficiary

33:42.440 --> 33:43.920
requires your signature.

33:44.550 --> 33:45.390
Yes,

33:45.510 --> 33:47.270
but I wasn't in the mood back then.

33:47.270 --> 33:47.750
To be honest,

33:47.750 --> 33:48.070
I

33:48.070 --> 33:49.200
didn't even read it carefully

33:49.200 --> 33:50.130
and just signed.

33:51.270 --> 33:51.870
By the way,

33:52.240 --> 33:53.590
she said

33:53.590 --> 33:56.250
she wanted to change the beneficiary
to her mom.

33:58.590 --> 34:00.520
Do you have her mom's information?

34:02.960 --> 34:04.550
What about the insurance broker?

34:04.550 --> 34:05.480
Do you know them?

34:05.640 --> 34:08.000
Yu Kexin handled all of this.

34:08.440 --> 34:09.710
When I was signing,

34:09.710 --> 34:11.400
I think I saw the broker once.

34:14.880 --> 34:15.880
That's not right.

34:16.710 --> 34:17.510
Attorney Zhou

34:18.000 --> 34:20.590
wouldn't bring this up for no reason.

34:28.550 --> 34:29.280
Ms. Yan,

34:31.320 --> 34:32.380
how's your acting?

34:34.550 --> 34:35.230
What?

34:38.159 --> 34:41.489
Welcome to Anning Property
Insurance Customer Service.

34:41.590 --> 34:43.840
Please hold while we connect you.

34:50.510 --> 34:53.800
Number 824 is at your service.

34:53.800 --> 34:55.920
Hello, thank you for waiting.

34:55.920 --> 34:57.760
How can I help you?

34:58.190 --> 34:58.880
Hello.

34:59.360 --> 35:00.920
I recently had a life insurance policy

35:00.920 --> 35:03.520
where the beneficiary was changed.

35:03.800 --> 35:05.400
I'd like to confirm

35:05.400 --> 35:06.360
whether the change

35:06.360 --> 35:07.480
was successful.

35:07.920 --> 35:08.480
Okay.

35:08.480 --> 35:10.400
May I have your name and ID number?

35:10.400 --> 35:12.510
-I'll write it for you.
-I'll check it for you.

35:12.510 --> 35:14.240
My name is Yu Kexin—

35:14.400 --> 35:15.590
Yu as in "niannianyouyu
(abundance every year),"

35:15.590 --> 35:16.440
Ke as in "keyi(okay),"

35:16.440 --> 35:18.630
and Xin as in "xinxinxiangrong
(flourishing)."

35:18.630 --> 35:19.920
My ID number is

35:20.550 --> 35:22.480
745201

35:22.710 --> 35:25.150
19890417

35:25.550 --> 35:26.550
8562.

35:26.960 --> 35:28.920
Please hold, I'll check for you.

35:28.920 --> 35:29.480
Okay.

35:30.400 --> 35:32.030
My records show

35:32.030 --> 35:33.920
that on April 23rd of this year,

35:33.920 --> 35:35.710
you changed the death beneficiary

35:35.710 --> 35:36.840
of your Anning Life Insurance

35:36.840 --> 35:37.920
to Yu Mingjie—

35:38.190 --> 35:39.590
Ming as in "guangming (brightness),"

35:39.590 --> 35:41.030
and Jie as in "haojie (hero),"

35:41.030 --> 35:41.960
is that correct?

35:42.630 --> 35:43.320
Yes.

35:49.190 --> 35:50.840
Could you help me confirm

35:50.840 --> 35:52.640
Yu Mingjie's ID number?

35:52.760 --> 35:53.640
Okay.

35:54.070 --> 35:55.850
Yu Mingjie's ID number is

35:56.070 --> 35:57.840
745201

35:58.190 --> 36:00.320
20160513

36:00.480 --> 36:01.600
8932.

36:02.960 --> 36:03.820
Okay.

36:04.070 --> 36:04.670
Thank you.

36:05.280 --> 36:06.210
I'll hang up now.

36:10.280 --> 36:11.450
Yu Mingjie?

36:12.360 --> 36:13.480
2016?

36:14.920 --> 36:16.120
He's only 3 years old.

36:16.630 --> 36:17.490
Do you know him?

36:18.800 --> 36:21.030
I don't know him at all.

36:22.190 --> 36:23.360
Such a huge fortune

36:23.360 --> 36:24.710
was left only to a child.

36:25.510 --> 36:27.370
He must be a close relative to her.

36:35.070 --> 36:37.150
I will definitely find him.

36:44.380 --> 36:46.460
[Dongchuan Public Security Bureau]

36:45.840 --> 36:46.760
Since the beginning of this year,

36:46.760 --> 36:48.670
multiple reports have come in
from across the province.

36:48.670 --> 36:49.920
A large number of victims

36:48.760 --> 36:50.930
[Report]

36:49.920 --> 36:51.070
were lured into investments

36:50.930 --> 36:51.640
[Lihai] [Dongchuan] [Longhai]

36:51.070 --> 36:52.150
through relationships

36:51.700 --> 36:53.670
[Report] [Kunxi] [Minggang]

36:52.320 --> 36:53.480
formed on social media,

36:53.480 --> 36:54.840
resulting in both financial
and emotional loss.

36:54.840 --> 36:56.920
Some victims were even driven to
the brink of collapse
and took their own lives.

36:56.920 --> 36:58.190
Leaders and experts
from the provincial department

36:58.190 --> 37:00.440
analyzed the cases
after linking them together.

37:00.440 --> 37:02.760
This is a new type of
telecommunications fraud

37:02.760 --> 37:04.480
packaged as emotional relationships.

37:04.480 --> 37:07.360
It's highly likely to be carried out
by the same criminal gang.

37:07.360 --> 37:09.660
We have successively caught
some underlings on the periphery.

37:07.750 --> 37:10.110
[Dongchuan Public Security Bureau]

37:09.960 --> 37:12.550
We can roughly determine that the gang
is located in the Pazion region,

37:12.550 --> 37:13.680
close to our border.

37:13.920 --> 37:15.630
They also recruit people in our country

37:14.930 --> 37:17.670
[Serve the people]

37:15.630 --> 37:17.710
by means of high-salary recruitment.

37:17.710 --> 37:18.800
On March 27th,

37:18.800 --> 37:20.630
the CID of the Lihai Municipal Bureau

37:20.630 --> 37:21.360
caught a technician

37:21.360 --> 37:24.150
responsible for
building fraudulent websites,

37:21.530 --> 37:23.830
[2. 18 Task Force]

37:24.150 --> 37:24.750
Cai Zhiyu,

37:24.960 --> 37:25.630
also known as Cai.

37:25.530 --> 37:26.820
[Cai Zhiyu]

37:26.510 --> 37:27.590
Finally, a big hole

37:27.590 --> 37:29.030
was torn in this gang.

37:29.150 --> 37:31.190
It also verified our judgment.

37:31.800 --> 37:33.460
According to his confession,

37:33.550 --> 37:35.650
Julong Company has about 300 people.

37:34.030 --> 37:38.620
[Supply Unit]
[Communications Unit]
[Technical Unit]
[Money Laundering Unit]

37:35.840 --> 37:37.670
The entire company has a
complete organizational structure

37:37.670 --> 37:38.710
with a clear division of labor.

37:38.710 --> 37:40.040
[Supply Unit—Collecting
Personal Information and Screening Users]

37:38.800 --> 37:39.660
The Supply Unit

37:39.880 --> 37:41.510
is responsible for
collecting personal information

37:41.510 --> 37:43.170
and screening precise users.

37:43.630 --> 37:44.510
The Communications Unit

37:44.510 --> 37:45.800
makes friends with the victims

37:44.590 --> 37:46.140
[Communications Unit—
Befriending Victims
and Building Emotional Trust]

37:45.800 --> 37:48.030
to cultivate relationships
and carry out fraud.

37:48.030 --> 37:48.840
The Technical Unit

37:48.840 --> 37:50.800
is responsible for
building virtual investment websites

37:50.800 --> 37:53.000
to absorb and transfer victims' funds.

37:53.670 --> 37:54.880
The aforementioned Cai Zhiyu

37:54.070 --> 37:55.380
[Technical Unit—Setting Up
Fake Investment Websites]

37:54.880 --> 37:56.480
was in charge of this department.

37:55.400 --> 37:56.330
[Absorbing the victims' funds]

37:56.510 --> 37:57.920
[Money Laundering Unit—Using Card Machines
and Various Methods]

37:56.590 --> 37:57.730
There is also a Money Laundering Unit.

37:57.730 --> 37:59.860
They use credit card machines
and various other methods

37:57.940 --> 37:59.250
[to break down the funds]

38:00.000 --> 38:02.920
to break down the funds layer by layer
before taking them out.

38:02.920 --> 38:04.630
Each department is isolated
from the others

38:04.630 --> 38:06.160
and real names are not used.

38:06.440 --> 38:07.800
Cai Zhiyu's rank was not high enough,

38:07.800 --> 38:08.880
so he didn't know

38:08.880 --> 38:10.760
the true identities
of the company's senior management.

38:10.760 --> 38:11.420
He only knew

38:11.550 --> 38:12.280
the chairman

38:12.400 --> 38:13.360
is nicknamed Master Bei.

38:12.560 --> 38:14.080
[Chairman, Master Bei]
[Top Figure—Relative]

38:13.400 --> 38:14.150
The second-in-command,

38:14.100 --> 38:15.900
[Second Brother—No. 2 Figure,
in Charge of Finance and Operations]

38:14.150 --> 38:15.480
nicknamed "Second Brother"
is his relative.

38:15.480 --> 38:18.840
He's mainly responsible for
the company's finances
and overall operations.

38:18.840 --> 38:21.320
There are also two
very important romance trainers.

38:21.290 --> 38:23.350
[Training Code name: Lu Ban]

38:21.320 --> 38:22.630
They work within the Communications Unit

38:22.630 --> 38:23.590
and are mainly responsible for

38:23.590 --> 38:26.000
developing and refining scam scripts.

38:27.190 --> 38:27.840
It's said that

38:27.840 --> 38:29.510
this method of romance before fraud

38:29.510 --> 38:30.880
was developed by them.

38:31.440 --> 38:32.590
One of the trainers

38:32.590 --> 38:33.650
is Pongsri Leekpa,

38:33.880 --> 38:34.910
from Pazion.

38:34.290 --> 38:36.020
[Xia Yi's passport]

38:35.110 --> 38:36.110
Known as Mr. Wang,

38:36.150 --> 38:37.070
he's excellent at Chinese,

38:37.070 --> 38:38.550
and suspected to be ethnic Chinese.

38:38.550 --> 38:40.250
He previously used the alias Xia Yi

38:40.250 --> 38:42.360
to commit fraud in our country.

38:42.710 --> 38:44.480
We found he has multiple

38:44.480 --> 38:46.070
entry and exit records at China Customs.

38:44.530 --> 38:49.460
[Xia Yi's passport] [Xia Yi's sketch
before plastic surgery]

38:46.070 --> 38:47.400
Every time he entered,

38:47.400 --> 38:48.630
he disappeared.

38:48.630 --> 38:49.630
We highly suspect

38:49.880 --> 38:51.410
he has a domestic identity.

38:52.590 --> 38:54.630
This Pongsri is highly likely
to have had plastic surgery.

38:54.630 --> 38:56.840
This is a reconstructed portrait of him
before surgery,

38:56.840 --> 38:59.280
drawn by experts based on
our analysis and estimates.

38:59.280 --> 39:01.360
Based on the portrait and age range,

39:01.510 --> 39:03.280
we screened

39:03.320 --> 39:05.360
more than 30 suspects
among those with a criminal record.

39:03.500 --> 39:05.390
[A sketch before Xia Yi's plastic surgery]
[Xia Yi's Entry and Exit Records]

39:06.150 --> 39:09.210
We are currently investigating
and eliminating them.

39:09.400 --> 39:10.400
Another trainer,

39:10.550 --> 39:11.480
nicknamed Lu Ban

39:11.520 --> 39:12.740
[Trainee Lu Ban, in charge of
the Communications Unit]

39:11.630 --> 39:12.710
is someone

39:12.710 --> 39:14.190
whose true identity we still don't know.

39:12.760 --> 39:14.420
[Development and upgrade
of the prank play]

39:14.760 --> 39:16.960
That's all we know about the whole case.

39:23.560 --> 39:26.420
[Dongchuan Public Security Bureau]

39:26.460 --> 39:29.220
[Scroll]

39:38.550 --> 39:40.390
You haven't left yet, Paw Patrol.

39:40.390 --> 39:41.200
[2. 18 Task Force]

39:44.360 --> 39:45.030
Sorry for

39:45.320 --> 39:46.150
waking you up.

39:48.440 --> 39:49.840
What did you just call me?

39:50.190 --> 39:50.960
Paw Patrol.

39:53.710 --> 39:55.030
Just kidding. Wait,

39:56.400 --> 39:58.880
but I think this nickname
suits you very well.

39:58.880 --> 39:59.960
We are all police.

40:00.250 --> 40:01.280
Every time you go out on a case,

40:01.280 --> 40:02.940
it's like Paw Patrol.

40:03.070 --> 40:04.920
Whenever there's trouble...

40:05.150 --> 40:05.960
BGM.

40:07.670 --> 40:08.330
Is it funny?

40:09.630 --> 40:10.590
It's okay, I think.

40:10.590 --> 40:11.320
Did I laugh?

40:12.070 --> 40:13.000
Why are you here?

40:14.670 --> 40:15.510
I

40:16.030 --> 40:17.280
thought of some clues.

40:17.280 --> 40:17.940
What clues?

40:19.360 --> 40:21.590
It's you, that...

40:21.590 --> 40:22.440
Tell me!

40:23.590 --> 40:24.170
No,

40:24.320 --> 40:25.150
look.

40:28.800 --> 40:29.510
Xia Yi

40:30.550 --> 40:31.500
and Lu Ban

40:31.670 --> 40:33.590
are both trainers in their company.

40:33.590 --> 40:35.150
So is it possible

40:36.110 --> 40:38.550
that Xia Yi and Lu Ban
went abroad together

40:38.550 --> 40:39.880
and came back together?

40:40.510 --> 40:41.320
Think about it,

40:41.320 --> 40:42.440
they are all acquaintances.

40:42.440 --> 40:44.030
It's very convenient

40:44.030 --> 40:45.030
to discuss lesson plans

40:45.030 --> 40:46.000
and upgrade the script on the plane.

40:46.000 --> 40:46.800
So I think...

40:47.510 --> 40:50.000
Excluding children, women
and the elderly over 60,

40:47.560 --> 40:48.450
[Entry and Exit Flight Records]

40:48.480 --> 40:49.050
[January 2019]

40:50.000 --> 40:51.110
this is the list of everyone

40:51.110 --> 40:52.840
on the same flight as Pongsri.

40:55.020 --> 40:56.060
[出入境航班信息记录表]

40:56.080 --> 40:56.700
[January 2019]

40:56.770 --> 40:59.520
[2. 18 Task Force]

41:03.360 --> 41:03.800
This...

41:03.800 --> 41:04.360
Did Cai

41:05.280 --> 41:06.800
go through them?

41:08.790 --> 41:10.480
He said there is no Lu Ban here.

41:16.190 --> 41:18.110
I thought I found a breakthrough.

41:18.840 --> 41:20.370
Got my hopes up for nothing.

41:20.480 --> 41:22.230
You see, I finally came here once,

41:22.230 --> 41:23.920
and I can't help with anything.

41:23.920 --> 41:25.360
It's quite awkward for me.

41:25.360 --> 41:27.630
I didn't expect you to be able to
help anyway.

41:27.630 --> 41:28.280
Exactly.

41:30.070 --> 41:31.320
In terms of CID techniques,

41:31.320 --> 41:31.960
interrogation methods,

41:31.960 --> 41:33.550
or even physical ability,

41:33.710 --> 41:34.880
you don't really rank.

41:34.880 --> 41:35.630
We called you here

41:35.630 --> 41:36.760
not for this reason.

41:37.320 --> 41:38.110
So direct.

41:40.190 --> 41:40.520
Wait.

41:41.190 --> 41:41.720
That day,

41:42.110 --> 41:43.440
you came to our station,

41:43.670 --> 41:44.870
stood behind my desk,

41:45.590 --> 41:47.480
looked at me
with a pleasant surprise and said,

41:47.480 --> 41:48.410
"Oh, no wonder."

41:49.840 --> 41:50.840
What does it mean?

42:03.980 --> 42:04.780
[Qingzhou Branch,
Lihai City Public Security Bureau]

42:04.810 --> 42:05.670
[Police File of Sanjie Police Station]

42:10.550 --> 42:12.550
I'm much fatter than in this photo.

42:12.550 --> 42:13.950
I was very thin back then.

42:14.440 --> 42:15.670
Later, I mainly focused on

42:15.670 --> 42:17.110
text and archive work.

42:17.280 --> 42:18.800
Everyone has their own strengths.

42:18.800 --> 42:21.360
Yes, so your value lies in

42:21.920 --> 42:23.190
that you are the only one among us

42:23.190 --> 42:25.510
who has had contact with Pongsri.

42:26.110 --> 42:28.550
He and Lu Ban are like ghosts to us,

42:28.760 --> 42:31.160
but to you, they are at least
real scammers.

42:32.070 --> 42:33.580
Think hard.

42:34.070 --> 42:35.880
Are there any details

42:35.880 --> 42:37.110
that you missed?

42:37.880 --> 42:39.150
Just stay here today

42:39.630 --> 42:40.110
to

42:40.110 --> 42:40.970
work overtime.

42:41.510 --> 42:42.920
Thanks for your hard work.

42:42.920 --> 42:44.580
Close the door when you leave.

42:52.550 --> 42:53.150
Okay.

42:54.890 --> 42:59.530
[The Dark Romance]

43:04.000 --> 43:06.400
[drift]

43:08.960 --> 43:11.360
Now you understand
why Yuan Ye stabbed you.

43:12.280 --> 43:13.810
She learned it from her mom.

43:14.530 --> 43:16.060
If you can't learn to drift,

43:16.470 --> 43:19.200
you'll just get into trouble
time and time again.

43:19.630 --> 43:20.920
You won't even know

43:21.070 --> 43:22.130
how you'll die.

43:22.210 --> 43:24.180
[Drifting–a driving technique,
also known as "drift"]

43:27.400 --> 43:28.630
Young Master,
you didn't fasten your seatbelt.

43:28.630 --> 43:29.360
Shut up!

43:29.950 --> 43:31.060
Just drive.
